| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **TypeScript typecheck** | Every push to any branch | npx tsc --noEmit — zero type errors allowed | Yes |
| **ESLint** | Every push | eslint src/ app/ — zero errors allowed | Yes |
| **Unit tests** | Every push | jest — all tests must pass | Yes |
| **RE safety gate queries** | Every push that touches supabase/ or src/services/re-client.ts | Run 3 SQL queries against foofoo-staging. Must return 0 rows each: (1) diet violations, (2) allergen violations, (3) Jain violations. | Yes — P0 release blocker |
| **Secret scan** | Every push | gitleaks scan — detect hardcoded API keys, passwords, JWTs | Yes |
| **Build check** | Push to apverse-labs-RE or main | EAS Build (development profile) — confirms build compiles for both platforms | Yes for staging. Manual for production. |

